                    <h3>OMDH: Advocating for Justice and Human Dignity</h3>

                </div>
                <div class="about-p">
                    <p>At the heart of our mission lies an unwavering commitment to justice, equality, and the protection of fundamental human rights. We advocate for the dignity and freedoms of all individuals, striving to create a world where every voice is heard, every right is upheld, and every person is empowered to live without fear or oppression.</p>
                    <button class="BtnPrimary" @onclick="navigateToProjects">Explore More</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        </div>
   
    <div class="Sec">
